<td data-index="1816">Elimination of the results of operations of a component of the business with cash flows that can be clearly distinguished and for which the elimination represents a strategic shift.</td>
<td data-index="1817">Sale by diversified company of major division that represents only activities in electronics industry. Food distributor that sells wholesale to supermarket chains and through fast-food restaurants decides to discontinue the division that sells to one of two classes of customers.</td>
<td data-index="1818">Show in separate section after continuing operations. <b data-index="1819">(Shown net of tax.)</b></td>
</tr>
