<td data-index="1936"> </td>
<td data-index="1937"> </td>
<td data-index="1938"><span class="right" style=" padding-right: 6em;" data-index="1939"><span class="bdr2" data-index="1940">$8,000</span></span></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<figcaption data-index="1941"><p data-index="1942"><span class="figureLabel" data-index="1943"><b data-index="1944"><a role="doc-backlink" href="#c04-fig-0016-1" data-index="1945" data-section-index="14" data-section-idref="c04-fig-0016-1" data-target-data-index="1889"><span style=" background-color: #127987; color: #FFFFFF;" data-index="1946">ILLUSTRATION 4.16</span></a></b> <b data-index="1947">Calculation of a Change in Accounting Principle</b></span></p></figcaption>
</figure>
<p data-index="1948"><a class="blue" id="c04-fig-0017-1" href="#c04-fig-0017" data-index="1949" data-section-index="14" data-section-idref="c04-fig-0017" data-target-data-index="1952"><b data-index="1950">Illustration 4.17</b></a><span data-index="1951"> shows the information Gaubert presented in its comparative income statements, based on a 30 percent tax rate.</span></p>
<figure id="c04-fig-0017" data-index="1952">
<div style=" background-color: #FFFDE9; padding: 1em; border: 1px solid #000;" data-index="1953">
<table class="bordernone" style=" width: 70%;" data-index="1954">
