</tr>
<tr data-index="2471">
<td data-index="2472">  Unrealized holding<br data-index="2473">   gain, net of tax</td>
<td data-index="2474"><span class="right" style=" padding-right: 2.5em;" data-index="2475"><span class="bdr1" data-index="2476"> 30,000</span></span></td>
<td data-index="2477"><span class="right" style=" padding-right: 2.5em;" data-index="2478"><span class="bdr1" data-index="2479"><span class="hidden" data-index="2480">0000000</span></span></span></td>
<td data-index="2481"><span class="right red" style=" padding-right: 2.5em;" data-index="2482"><span class="bdr1" data-index="2483"> 30,000</span></span></td>
<td data-index="2484"><span class="right" style=" padding-right: 2.5em;" data-index="2485"><span class="bdr1" data-index="2486"><span class="hidden" data-index="2487">0000000</span></span></span></td>
</tr>
<tr data-index="2488">
<td data-index="2489">Ending balance</td>
<td data-index="2490"><span class="right" style=" padding-right: 2.5em;" data-index="2491"><span class="bdr2" data-index="2492">$550,000</span></span></td>
<td data-index="2493"><span class="right" style=" padding-right: 2.5em;" data-index="2494"><span class="bdr2" data-index="2495">$160,000</span></span></td>
<td data-index="2496"><span class="right red" style=" padding-right: 2.5em;" data-index="2497"><span class="bdr2" data-index="2498">$90,000</span></span></td>
<td data-index="2499"><span class="right" style=" padding-right: 2.5em;" data-index="2500"><span class="bdr2" data-index="2501">$300,000</span></span></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<figcaption data-index="2502"><p data-index="2503"><span class="figureLabel" data-index="2504"><b data-index="2505"><a role="doc-backlink" href="#c04-fig-0022-1" data-index="2506" data-section-index="14" data-section-idref="c04-fig-0022-1" data-target-data-index="2417"><span style=" background-color: #127987; color: #FFFFFF;" data-index="2507">ILLUSTRATION 4.22</span></a></b> <b data-index="2508">Presentation of Comprehensive Income in Stockholders’ Equity Statement</b></span></p></figcaption>
</figure>
</section>
<section id="h3_000068" data-index="2509">
<h3 data-index="2510"><span class="red" data-index="2511">Balance Sheet Presentation</span></h3>
<p data-index="2512">Regardless of reporting in one statement or two, V. Gill reports <span class="glossTerm" data-index="2513"><span class="blue" data-index="2514"><b data-index="2515">accumulated other comprehensive income</b></span></span> of $90,000 in the stockholders’ equity section of the balance sheet as shown in <a class="blue" id="c04-fig-0023-1" href="#c04-fig-0023" data-index="2516" data-section-index="14" data-section-idref="c04-fig-0023" data-target-data-index="2518"><b data-index="2517">Illustration 4.23</b></a>.</p>
<figure id="c04-fig-0023" data-index="2518">
<div style=" background-color: #FFFDE9; padding: 1em; border: 1px solid #000;" data-index="2519">
<table class="bordernone" style=" width: 70%;" data-index="2520">
<thead data-index="2521">
<tr data-index="2522">
<td colspan="2" class="bdr1" data-index="2523"><span class="center" data-index="2524">V. Gill Inc.<br data-index="2525">Balance Sheet<br data-index="2526">As of December 31, 2020<br data-index="2527">(Stockholders’ Equity Section)</span></td>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody data-index="2528">
<tr data-index="2529">
