<h4 data-index="3566"><span class="red" data-index="3567">Instructions</span></h4>
<p class="latin1" data-index="3568"><span class="label" data-index="3569"><b data-index="3570">a.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Prepare an income statement for the year 2020 using the multiple-step form. Common shares outstanding for 2020 total 40,550 (000 omitted).</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="3571"><span class="label" data-index="3572"><b data-index="3573">b.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Prepare an income statement for the year 2020 using the single-step form.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="3574"><span class="label" data-index="3575"><b data-index="3576">c.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Which one do you prefer? Discuss.</p>
<p id="E4.6_1" data-index="3577"><b data-index="3578"><span class="codeColorBlue2" data-index="3579">E4.6</span></b> <span class="red" data-index="3580"><b data-index="3581">(LO <a href="#h3_0002" data-index="3582" data-section-index="14" data-section-idref="h3_0002" data-target-data-index="352">2</a>, <a href="#h3_0003" data-index="3583" data-section-index="14" data-section-idref="h3_0003" data-target-data-index="1029">3</a>)</b></span> <span class="bold" data-index="3584">(</span><span class="bold" data-index="3585">Multiple-Step Statement</span><span class="bold" data-index="3586">)</span> <span data-index="3587">The following balances were taken from the books of Alonzo Corp. on December 31, 20</span>20.</p>
<table data-index="3588">
<tbody data-index="3589">
<tr data-index="3590">
