<td data-index="4460">Dividends declared on preferred stock</td>
<td data-index="4461"><span class="right" data-index="4462">80,000</span></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p data-index="4463">Dickinson Company decided to discontinue its entire wholesale operations (considered a discontinued operation) and to retain its manufacturing operations. On September 15, Dickinson sold the wholesale operations to Rogers Company. During 2020, there were 500,000 shares of common stock outstanding all year.</p>
<h4 data-index="4464"><span class="red" data-index="4465">Instructions</span></h4>
