<p class="latin2" data-index="5065"><span class="label" data-index="5066"><b data-index="5067">3.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> “Adjustment required for correction of an error” was a result of a change in estimate (useful life of certain assets reduced to 8 years and a catch-up adjustment made).</p>
<p class="latin2" data-index="5068"><span class="label" data-index="5069"><b data-index="5070">4.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Nerwin Company disclosed earnings per common share for net income in the notes to the financial statements.</p>
