<p data-index="5923"><span class="blue" data-index="5924"><b data-index="5925">CE4.1</b></span> Access the glossary (“Master Glossary”) to answer the following.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="5926"><span class="label" data-index="5927"><b data-index="5928">a.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> What is a change in accounting estimate?</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="5929"><span class="label" data-index="5930"><b data-index="5931">b.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> How is a change in accounting principle distinguished from a “change in accounting estimate effected by a change in accounting principle”?</p>
