<p data-index="5939"><span class="codeColorBlue2" data-index="5940"><b data-index="5941">CE4.3</b></span> What guidance does the SEC provide for public companies with respect to the reporting of the “effect of preferred stock dividends and accretion of carrying amount of preferred stock on earnings per share”?</p>
