<p data-index="6199">If Telaris uses the function-of-expense approach, its income statement is as follows.</p>
<figure data-index="6200">
<div style=" background-color: #FFFDE9; padding: 1em; border: 1px solid #000;" data-index="6201">
<table class="bordernone" style=" width: 50%;" data-index="6202">
